21#define RRTYPE_KEY_ATTRIBUTES \
22 ( DNS_RDATATYPEATTR_ATCNAME | DNS_RDATATYPEATTR_ZONECUTAUTH )

24static inline isc_result_t
25generic_fromtext_key(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
26 isc_token_t token;
27 dns_secalg_t alg;
28 dns_secproto_t proto;
29 dns_keyflags_t flags;
30
31 UNUSED(type);
32 UNUSED(rdclass);
33 UNUSED(origin);
34 UNUSED(options);
35 UNUSED(callbacks);
36
37 /* flags */
38 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
39 false));
40 RETTOK(dns_keyflags_fromtext(&flags, &token.value.as_textregion));
41 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(flags, target));
42
43 /* protocol */
44 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
45 false));
46 RETTOK(dns_secproto_fromtext(&proto, &token.value.as_textregion));
47 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &proto, 1));
48
49 /* algorithm */
50 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
51 false));
52 RETTOK(dns_secalg_fromtext(&alg, &token.value.as_textregion));
53 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &alg, 1));
54
55 /* No Key? */
56 if ((flags & 0xc000) == 0xc000)
57 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
58
59 return (isc_base64_tobuffer(lexer, target, -2));
60}
61
62static inline isc_result_t
63generic_totext_key(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
64 isc_region_t sr;
65 char buf[sizeof("[key id = 64000]")];
66 unsigned int flags;
67 unsigned char algorithm;
68 char algbuf[DNS_NAME_FORMATSIZE];
69 const char *keyinfo;
70 isc_region_t tmpr;
71
72 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
73
74 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
75
76 /* flags */
77 flags = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
78 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
79 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", flags);
80 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
81 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
82 if ((flags & DNS_KEYFLAG_KSK) != 0) {
83 if (flags & DNS_KEYFLAG_REVOKE)
84 keyinfo = "revoked KSK";
85 else
86 keyinfo = "KSK";
87 } else
88 keyinfo = "ZSK";
89
90
91 /* protocol */
92 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", sr.base[0]);
93 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
94 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
95 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
96
97 /* algorithm */
98 algorithm = sr.base[0];
99 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", algorithm);
100 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
101 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
102
103 /* No Key? */
104 if ((flags & 0xc000) == 0xc000)
105 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
106
107 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_RRCOMMENT) != 0 &&
108 algorithm == DNS_KEYALG_PRIVATEDNS) {
109 dns_name_t name;
110 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
111 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
112 dns_name_format(&name, algbuf, sizeof(algbuf));
113 } else {
114 dns_secalg_format((dns_secalg_t) algorithm, algbuf,
115 sizeof(algbuf));
116 }
117
118 /* key */
119 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
120 RETERR(str_totext(" (", target));
121 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
122
123 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_NOCRYPTO) == 0) {
124 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
125 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, 60, "", target));
126 else
127 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, tctx->width - 2,
128 tctx->linebreak, target));
129 } else {
130 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &tmpr);
131 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "[key id = %u]",
132 dst_region_computeid(&tmpr));
133 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
134 }
135
136 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_RRCOMMENT) != 0)
137 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
138 else if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
139 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
140
141 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
142 RETERR(str_totext(")", target));
143
144 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_RRCOMMENT) != 0) {
145
146 if (rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey ||
147 rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey) {
148 RETERR(str_totext(" ; ", target));
149 RETERR(str_totext(keyinfo, target));
150 }
151 RETERR(str_totext("; alg = ", target));
152 RETERR(str_totext(algbuf, target));
153 RETERR(str_totext(" ; key id = ", target));
154 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &tmpr);
155 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u",
156 dst_region_computeid(&tmpr));
157 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
158 }
159 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
160}

162static inline isc_result_t
163generic_fromwire_key(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
164 unsigned char algorithm;
165 isc_region_t sr;
166
167 UNUSED(type);
168 UNUSED(rdclass);
169 UNUSED(dctx);
170 UNUSED(options);
171
172 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
173 if (sr.length < 4)
174 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
175
176 algorithm = sr.base[3];
177 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 4));
178 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
179 isc_buffer_forward(source, 4);
180
181 if (algorithm == DNS_KEYALG_PRIVATEDNS) {
182 dns_name_t name;
183 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
184 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
185 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
186 }
187
188 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
189 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
190 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
191}

194fromtext_key(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
195
196 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_key);
197

199 options, target, callbacks));

220static inline isc_result_t
221towire_key(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
222 isc_region_t sr;
223
224 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
225 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_key);
226 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
227
228 UNUSED(cctx);
229
230 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
231 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
232}

234static inline int
235compare_key(ARGS_COMPARE) {
236 isc_region_t r1;
237 isc_region_t r2;
238
239 REQUIRE(rdata1 != NULL);
240 REQUIRE(rdata2 != NULL);
241 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
242 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
243 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_key);
244 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
245 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
246
247 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
248 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
249 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
250}
251
252static inline isc_result_t
253generic_fromstruct_key(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
254 dns_rdata_key_t *key = source;
255
256 REQUIRE(key != NULL);
257 REQUIRE(key->common.rdtype == type);
258 REQUIRE(key->common.rdclass == rdclass);
259
260 UNUSED(type);
261 UNUSED(rdclass);
262
263 /* Flags */
264 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(key->flags, target));
265
266 /* Protocol */
267 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(key->protocol, target));
268
269 /* Algorithm */
270 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(key->algorithm, target));
271
272 /* Data */
273 return (mem_tobuffer(target, key->data, key->datalen));
274}
275
276static inline isc_result_t
277generic_tostruct_key(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
278 dns_rdata_key_t *key = target;
279 isc_region_t sr;
280
281 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
282 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
283
284 REQUIRE(key != NULL);
285 REQUIRE(key->common.rdclass == rdata->rdclass);
286 REQUIRE(key->common.rdtype == rdata->type);
287 REQUIRE(!ISC_LINK_LINKED(&key->common, link));
288
289 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
290
291 /* Flags */
292 if (sr.length < 2)
293 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
294 key->flags = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
295 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
296
297 /* Protocol */
298 if (sr.length < 1)
299 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
300 key->protocol = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
301 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
302
303 /* Algorithm */
304 if (sr.length < 1)
305 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
306 key->algorithm = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
307 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
308
309 /* Data */
310 key->datalen = sr.length;
311 key->data = mem_maybedup(mctx, sr.base, key->datalen);
312 if (key->data == NULL)
313 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
314
315 key->mctx = mctx;
316 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
317}
318
319static inline void
320generic_freestruct_key(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
321 dns_rdata_key_t *key = (dns_rdata_key_t *) source;
322
323 REQUIRE(key != NULL);
324
325 if (key->mctx == NULL)
326 return;
327
328 if (key->data != NULL)
329 isc_mem_free(key->mctx, key->data);
330 key->mctx = NULL;
331}
332
333static inline isc_result_t
334fromstruct_key(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
335
336 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_key);
337
338 return (generic_fromstruct_key(rdclass, type, source, target));
339}
340
341static inline isc_result_t
342tostruct_key(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
343 dns_rdata_key_t *key = target;
344
345 REQUIRE(key != NULL);
346 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
347 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_key);
348
349 key->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
350 key->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
351 ISC_LINK_INIT(&key->common, link);
352
353 return (generic_tostruct_key(rdata, target, mctx));
354}
355
356static inline void
357freestruct_key(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
358 dns_rdata_key_t *key = (dns_rdata_key_t *) source;
359
360 REQUIRE(key != NULL);
361 REQUIRE(key->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_key);
362
363 generic_freestruct_key(source);
364}

379static inline isc_result_t
380digest_key(ARGS_DIGEST) {
381 isc_region_t r;
382
383 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
384 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_key);
385
386 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
387
388 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
389}
